WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.179 --> 00:00:01.913
I'm here with you again.

00:00:02.260 --> 00:00:04.714
I'm going to do another prayer video here.

00:00:04.714 --> 00:00:24.820
It's just really on my heart because I feel such an urgency for many of you who don't know how to pray effectively in an unknown tongue and flow with the Spirit.

00:00:27.922 --> 00:00:36.360
You are learning how to flow in the rivers that I've talked to you about, learning how to go into the deep water in intercessory prayer.

00:00:36.360 --> 00:00:41.160
There is a level of intercessory prayer that goes deeper and deeper when you start flowing with Him.

00:00:41.160 --> 00:00:48.400
It's not shallow; you start losing all your needs as far as what's on your heart, and you start praying the Father's heart.

00:00:48.720 --> 00:01:03.839
When you start praying the Father's heart and seeking His face—as it says, 'Seek ye first the kingdom and all these things will be added unto you'—whatever you have need of is at His throne, sitting at His feet.

00:01:03.839 --> 00:01:14.560
When you seek His face daily and listen to Him, there is a Holy Ghost flow.

00:01:14.560 --> 00:01:29.189
If you just pray in the Spirit for 30 minutes a day—you may say you don't have enough time to pray an hour—I encourage you to just pray 30 minutes a day in tongues.

00:01:31.611 --> 00:01:43.140
Even just praying along with these videos and flowing with the Holy Ghost, the Word talks about how the Holy Spirit is filling you, but you have to move your tongue.

00:01:43.635 --> 00:01:44.895
You have to move out by faith.

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:55.860
You don't just sit there and wait for the Holy Spirit to move your tongue.

00:01:59.667 --> 00:02:02.414
You don't say, 'Okay, Holy Spirit, let's pray in tongues,' and then wait.

00:02:04.200 --> 00:02:05.460
You have to put your boat into motion.

00:02:06.719 --> 00:02:11.209
You have to start letting Him go over you and start praying in the Spirit.

00:02:19.319 --> 00:02:19.672
You have to speak it out and let Him have control of your tongue and your thoughts.

00:02:19.672 --> 00:02:26.782
If you're worried about whether you're speaking it right, do what we're about to do here with me.

00:02:28.319 --> 00:02:36.164
You can start by mimicking it with your tongue—just speaking with it is what I'm trying to say—and let the Holy Spirit flow through you.

00:02:36.164 --> 00:02:42.877
It may sound like babbling, but you're going to hit that gusher—that Holy Ghost gusher—and you're going to start flowing in the Spirit.

00:02:43.980 --> 00:02:44.204
Just try.

00:02:44.204 --> 00:02:53.893
You've got to let the Holy Spirit take over; you can't just sit there and wait for Him to move your mouth.

00:02:55.166 --> 00:02:58.996
Just as faith without works is dead, you have to add your faith to it.

00:03:00.283 --> 00:03:02.630
You have to believe God for your miracle and your healing.

00:03:03.679 --> 00:03:12.060
You've got to speak to your mountain and your circumstances; you've got to speak and call those things that be not as though they were.

00:03:12.060 --> 00:03:17.670
You've got to operate your faith just like in any area of your life.

00:03:17.670 --> 00:03:27.847
If you're believing for finances, you sow a seed and give to the church or wherever you're getting fed, and you believe God for a harvest because that is your faith in action.

00:03:27.847 --> 00:03:37.474
Whether you're sowing a seed or acting—maybe you can't move your arms, or if you're a quadriplegic, you try to move your eyes—you've got to put your faith into something.

00:03:38.923 --> 00:03:41.000
Faith without works is dead; you've got to move.

00:03:46.766 --> 00:03:47.049
So that's what I'm trying to tell you today.

00:03:52.299 --> 00:03:57.099
We're going to pray with Sister Billy and a lot of others here at this church.

00:03:57.739 --> 00:03:59.842
I made this video to help people.

00:03:59.842 --> 00:04:09.720
If you're dry, or if you don't like praying by yourself, you can put this on your phone in your car on the way to work and pray in the Holy Ghost.

00:04:13.460 --> 00:04:18.753
Or pray when you get home or during your quiet time.

00:04:23.113 --> 00:04:23.380
Just get in this river.

00:04:29.064 --> 00:04:34.410
This is a time where, if you want to see the supernatural in your life, you've got to put your faith to it and pray in the Spirit.

00:04:38.988 --> 00:04:39.222
It doesn't just happen; you've got to pray and intercede.

00:04:39.222 --> 00:04:42.231
