There is another source of water then that comes from the Earth, from us, up from our bellies.

01:17:11.902 --> 01:17:18.000
This one also comes from God, but out of our hearts.

01:17:30.077 --> 01:17:33.852
And Jesus said you can come to Me and drink, and when you come to Him and drink, out of your belly would flow rivers.

01:17:47.910 --> 01:17:54.660
What was interesting is that actually, if there is enough water coming to a riverbed through rain—and your prayers may seem to you like a drop of water—enough of those drops of water will cause a wall of water.

01:17:54.660 --> 01:18:00.651
In Australia, they called it an inland tsunami.

01:18:00.651 --> 01:18:04.215
How does that even happen?

01:18:20.813 --> 01:18:47.450
You know of tsunamis out on the ocean, and we had that some years ago in that part of the world, but this was an inland tsunami that came from rain, from drops of water.

01:19:10.425 --> 01:19:15.493
It filled riverbeds—it filled dead riverbeds—and this one was inland from where we live, up in the mountains in a place called Toowoomba.

01:19:15.493 --> 01:19:25.170
I watched this, and I want you to see it.

01:19:25.170 --> 01:19:46.140
When I saw this, it moved me because it pictured in a small way what I was seeing in my spirit.

01:19:46.140 --> 01:20:12.980
If believers would come to Him and drink and pray in the Holy Ghost, our contribution of rivers, our convergence of rivers, makes a vast supply of water that moves things.

01:20:12.980 --> 01:20:24.800
When we pray together, it changes things that we cannot change, and we let the river do the work.

01:20:30.180 --> 01:20:40.410
I didn't know it, but rivers can be at such an amount that they are a tsunami supply.

01:20:40.410 --> 01:20:54.853
If you go ahead and roll that and just look at it—you don't have to turn on the sound—look at that.

01:20:54.853 --> 01:21:15.807
This stream of water was just a little runoff ditch, and now it is moving.

01:21:28.120 --> 01:21:28.440
Of course, you know that floodwater is usually dirty water.

01:21:28.440 --> 01:21:41.388
The river that comes out of Jesus Christ that we come to Him and drink is crystal clear, and it is life flowing today; it's coming fast.

01:21:41.388 --> 01:21:42.252
It's life.

01:21:42.252 --> 01:21:52.100
That word, Pastor George, that you got for this meeting about persistence in prayer—just keep praying.

01:21:52.100 --> 01:22:06.240
Now, it would take a group of men to move a car if they wanted to move it, but if there gets to be enough water, things that you cannot move just begin to float.

01:22:06.240 --> 01:22:07.212
Obstinate things.

01:22:07.212 --> 01:22:17.070
People are moved away from what they need to be moved away from and carried to what they need to be carried to.

01:22:17.070 --> 01:22:21.831
There goes another one floating down the river.

01:22:21.831 --> 01:22:25.320
We can move it with the Holy Ghost.

01:22:25.320 --> 01:22:29.053
He needs to move that car real quick.

01:22:29.053 --> 01:22:32.413
That one wants to get out of the flow.

01:22:32.413 --> 01:22:36.780
Look, there are some more—that persistence, perpetual persistence, drinking from Jesus.

01:22:36.780 --> 01:22:40.410
He said out of your innermost being would flow rivers.

01:22:40.410 --> 01:22:44.028
Praise God, not for destruction, but out of the belly of living water.

01:22:44.028 --> 01:22:45.108
Thank You, Jesus.

01:22:45.108 --> 01:22:53.205
Now, that one was a real stubborn one, and there are some stubborn situations, but the river can do the work.

01:22:53.205 --> 01:22:53.640
Hallelujah.

01:22:53.640 --> 01:23:11.190
Pastor George, I believe that we come to Jesus and drink from those reserves—those reservoirs that have been laid up for this time—and we have tsunamis of rivers and we also, in addition, have that wave that's coming from the very heart of God.

01:23:11.190 --> 01:23:15.960
Can we just go ahead and start praying in the Holy Ghost?

01:23:18.067 --> 01:23:18.320
We drink.

01:23:18.320 --> 01:23:21.023
Well, that was a good prayer session.

01:23:21.023 --> 01:23:25.809
I just wanted to thank you all for joining me.

01:23:25.809 --> 01:23:30.020
I know that was long, about an hour and 15 minutes, but the illustration at the end about how we can flow as a group...

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
like I said, the last video I did had 10,000 hits.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
If everybody prayed, even if it lasted 15 minutes, just think of what we could do as a body joined together.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
There's power in unity when we pray as a family, and we can flow.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
The greater the river coming out of us, the greater the river of living water out of all of us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Think of all those rivers combined.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
What that does in the spirit realm, pushing stuff for the Lord in the world!

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.800
When we join together, we are so powerful because it's not just one little stream flowing; it's a river, and then it carries a river out of you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
All those rivers together create one massive tsunami river.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
I just want to praise God for an opportunity to be able to pray together like this.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
It really blesses me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
I hope this blessed you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
If it did and you're still watching, please comment down below; tell me if you want more videos like this.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
I need to know what direction you all like.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.050
I know what the Holy Ghost is telling me, but if you like this more, or do you like Brother Hagin, or what?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
I'm trying to do different people, different rivers, and different flows of the Holy Ghost.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
Instead of just taking one river, I'm trying to go with a whole different bunch of rivers.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
I hope this blessed you today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Thank you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Please like my video, subscribe, and ring that notification bell.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
Thank you for all the gifts, all the love, and the kindness that you've showed my family.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
We love you, and Jesus loves you, and we thank you for joining us today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
You all have a blessed and wonderful day, and we'll see you next time.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
